It's an example of vermiculture
in these plastic bins.

119
00:07:19,071 --> 00:07:24,732
Weekly, about 10% -- 
so a corner of each bin is harvested

120
00:07:24,732 --> 00:07:26,814
and the worms are removed.

121
00:07:26,814 --> 00:07:29,361
This worms are then sold as shrimp feed

122
00:07:29,361 --> 00:07:33,501
or processed to medicinal capsules
for human consumption.

123
