and you see it's quite easy 
to just use one corner in the neighborhood

125
00:07:39,891 --> 00:07:44,922
and to stack this with different boxes
where vermicomposting is done.

126
00:07:45,762 --> 00:07:48,513
Here an example from rural India

127
00:07:48,513 --> 00:07:52,764
where the vermi bins are made
with cement rings.

128
